OL,3,C'Paddington the Musical' and 'Into The
OL,4,CWoods' up for 11 Olivier Awards each
OL,6,F'Paddington The Musical' has received
OL,7,F11 Olivier Award nominations, tied
OL,8,Fwith 'Into The Woods'.
OL,10,FThe nominations for British theatre's
OL,11,Fmost prestigious honours see
OL,12,F'Paddington the Musical' and 'Into The
OL,13,FWoods' lead with way- with eleven
OL,14,Fnominations each.
OL,16,FThe Olivier Award nominations were
OL,17,Fannounced today, ahead of the awards
OL,18,Fin April which celebrate their 50th
OL,19,Fanniversary this year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
