OL,3,C'Paddington the Musical' and 'Into The
OL,4,CWoods' up for 11 Olivier Awards each
OL,6,F'Paddington The Musical' was written
OL,7,Fby McFly's Tom Fletcher and has
OL,8,Freceived rave reviews since opening in
OL,9,FDecember.
OL,11,FIts nominations include best new
OL,12,Fmusical, best actor in a musical for
OL,13,FJames Hameed and Arti Shah ` who
OL,14,Fjointly perform the role of the bear `
OL,15,Ftwo nominations for best actress in a
OL,16,Fsupporting role in a musical (Amy
OL,17,FBooth-Steel and Victoria Hamilton-
OL,18,FBarritt), the Sir Peter Hall award for
OL,19,Fbest director (Luke Sheppard), and
OL,20,Fbest set design.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
