PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772745124
OL,3,C'Paddington the Musical' and 'Into The
OL,4,CWoods' up for 11 Olivier Awards each
OL,6,FIn many categories, it is up against
OL,7,F'Into The Woods' which is currently
OL,8,Frunning at London's Bridge Theatre.
OL,9,FIts nominations include best actor in
OL,10,Fa musical (Jamie Parker), two
OL,11,Fnominations for best actor in a
OL,12,Fsupporting role in a musical (Jo
OL,13,FFoster and Oliver Saville), and the
OL,14,FSir Peter Hall Award for best director
OL,15,F(Jordan Fein).
OL,17,FRachel Zegler is another big name who
OL,18,Fhas been nominated for best actress in
OL,19,Fa musical for her West End debut in
OL,20,FEvita at The London Palladium.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
