OL,3,C'Paddington the Musical' and 'Into The
OL,4,CWoods' up for 11 Olivier Awards each
OL,6,FHer performance made headlines last
OL,7,Fyear, when she would leave the stage
OL,8,Fduring each show to perform 'Don't Cry
OL,9,FFor Me Argentina' on a balcony to the
OL,10,Fgeneral public.
OL,12,FAn Olivier Award spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"In what has been another outstanding
OL,15,Fyear on London's stages, bold new
OL,16,Fwriting has sat alongside revelatory
OL,17,Frevivals, large-scale spectacle and
OL,18,Fintimate studio work, reflecting the
OL,19,Fbreadth and vitality of the UK's world-
OL,20,Fleading theatre industry.
