OL,3,C'Paddington the Musical' and 'Into The
OL,4,CWoods' up for 11 Olivier Awards each
OL,6,F"International stars and homegrown
OL,7,Ftalent alike have lit up our stages,
OL,8,Fwhile creatives have pushed boundaries
OL,9,Fwith remarkable imagination and skill."
OL,11,FSee the full list of this years
OL,12,Fnominee's below:
OL,14,FBest musical revival
OL,16,FBest revival
OL,18,FBest actress
OL,20,FBest actress in a musical
